{"tid":2007320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］科大指校內的周梓樂追悼會違法，將處分及報警處理！","createTime":"2020-05-08T09:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T12:51:48.000Z","uid":219007,"like":17,"dislike":239,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bf6f46eb7eb6fa5bb2c7a46ef541a792439a5a","tid":2007320,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ca1333dd2be82c3564dfdce501bfb97eb3ffb1","tid":2007320,"uid":219007,"like":59,"dislike":35,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"科大校方今早突向全校師生發電郵，以疫情為由禁止學生參與校內公眾集會，威脅會按「限聚令」向執法部門舉報及作出紀律處分。科大學生會則稱追悼會將照常舉行。<br />\n<br />\n校方於電郵中表示，基於公共衞生，不會批准校園內舉行任何公眾集會。校方又引述「限聚令」條款，指組織及參與校園內集會屬違法，違者可判罰款及入獄，聲稱將會向有關執法部門舉報違法行為，並向違規科大師生作出紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會指，周梓樂逝世半周年追悼會將照常於今晚6時舉行，但無法安排非科大人士進入校園，將於追悼會結束後在校園範圍外見記者講述事件。"},{"pid":"dd0f595a6804b4c6ba5e5af9cd15c71c34a53b2f","tid":2007320,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">link?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"bdde72fcc6617ce6db702eabfac88418bb1d988e","tid":2007320,"uid":33508,"like":147,"dislike":3,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"食屎啦史維<br />\n你無資格為梓樂喊啊"},{"pid":"c57197d89dcf2b36529c864133495b3c4ab5bd69","tid":2007320,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19ca1333dd2be82c3564dfdce501bfb97eb3ffb1","tid":2007320,"uid":219007,"like":59,"dislike":35,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"科大校方今早突向全校師生發電郵，以疫情為由禁止學生參與校內公眾集會，威脅會按「限聚令」向執法部門舉報及作出紀律處分。科大學生會則稱追悼